{"id":11462,"date":"2013-01-17T16:22:29","date_gmt":"2013-01-17T21:22:29","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=11462"},"modified":"2025-03-22T09:15:07","modified_gmt":"2025-03-22T05:15:07","slug":"prophet-protects-woman-from-husband","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/17\/prophet-protects-woman-from-husband\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Divorce: The Prophet protects wife from abusive husband"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The wife of Al-Walid ibn &#8216;Uqbah came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and she complained to him saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah! Al-Walid has beaten me!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Say to him: He has protected me<\/b>.\u201d She did not stay but for a while until she returned and she said, \u201cHe did not give me anything but more beatings!\u201d The Prophet tore a piece of cloth from his shirt and he said, \u201c<b>Say to him: Verily, the Messenger of Allah has given me his protection.<\/b>\u201d She did not stay but for a while until she returned and she said, \u201cHe did not give me anything but more beatings!\u201d The Prophet raised his hands and he said, \u201c<b>O Allah, you must deal with Al-Walid, for he has sinned against me twice<\/b>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 1303<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><i>Sahih\u00a0<\/i><\/strong>(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u064d\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652